gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

Such devotion as that of Pratap, which was spoken by Krishna Sharma's father; 
Now I will do it, taking shelter in beautiful and great Lord.

Mounted the horse with pride and joy, sounds of drums in rhythm play; 

Tied the chariot to the dawn, yoked the horses to go; 
Walks one step at a time, another takes flight.

Here is the translation:

Ude Abeer Gulaal Teel Re, Thai Rahi Che Rangdana Ni Rel Re;
Em Ramya Jamya Rudi Riite Re, Pachi Krishna Sharma Bolya Prete Re;
